{"tid":395314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"目前為止人類有無係風眼入面影過相？","createTime":"2017-09-10T16:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T15:00:18.000Z","uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b217e0665f54ae3748837103aee832af028d74fd","tid":395314,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"係咪連遙距影都無？<br />\n歷史上得兩個人入過去出返黎<br />\n<a href=\"http://science.howstuffworks.com/nature/natural-disasters/eye-of-tornado1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.howstuffworks.com%2Fnature%2Fnatural-disasters%2Feye-of-tornado1.htm&d=mLtEjXnqUXMZ4wBHwMEEwf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3f3ad69b\" target=\"_blank\">http://science.howstuffworks.com/nature/natural-disasters/eye-of-tornado1.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d048dd0b13a6bc1ba99a6c503dc0bbeba5ac2703","tid":395314,"uid":44569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:29:06.000Z","msg":"被形容為大西洋10年來最強颶風「艾爾瑪」（Irma），預料趨向美國佛羅里達州。美國國家海洋及大氣管理局（NOAA）有英勇的「風暴獵人」，駕駛偵察機穿越「艾爾瑪」的風眼，近距拍攝它的情況，讓當局得到寶貴的資料分析「艾爾瑪」的路徑及強度等。<br />\n<br />\nNOAA的一班「風暴獵人」自過去周末開始，已多次飛越「艾爾瑪」收集有用資料，團隊周二發佈的影片驚心動魄。影片可見他們駕駛螺旋偵察機飛進「艾爾瑪」的風眼牆（eyewall），狂風及暴雨吹打著機身，突然間機外變得相對風平浪靜，因為偵察機已進入了「艾爾瑪」的風眼。<br />\n<br />\n今次穿越「艾爾瑪」的是改良版的P-3獵戶座（Orion）偵察機「WP-3D Orion」，機師在飛近風暴後釋放載有GPS的探測儀，用來搜集風向、風速、濕度等資料，讓專家分析出風暴的結構及強度；機上亦裝設了特別的雷達系統如「多普勒雷達」（Doppler radar）等，全方位掃描風暴形態。<br />\n<br />\nNOAA表示偵察機本周仍會多次飛近「艾爾瑪」，以取得更多資料分析風暴詳情。美國共有兩隊官方「風暴獵人」，除了NOAA屬下的一隊，還有隸屬美國空軍的一隊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170906/57176287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170906%2F57176287&d=mLtEjXnqUXMZ4wBHwMEEwf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4983bc3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170906%2F57176287&h=80156e32\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170906/57176287</a>"},{"pid":"e4710967028e09e50149478d95d029a97c81cd53","tid":395314,"uid":46587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"留名睇uncle幅相"},{"pid":"ade50ac7f2bed08a3e795a7a818e637f37710018","tid":395314,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:43:17.000Z","msg":"條 link 係龍捲風風眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f92191db93acff8fde9ac9168f335fed7473251","tid":395314,"uid":38795,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:45:50.000Z","msg":"uncle成日去"},{"pid":"ad50b7fda4b52113c9dc1dd3f298f99f3eb5a6eb","tid":395314,"uid":125237,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/135200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F135200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=745cd0ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e0edd6a1153ee505ee1ec0e50a500ab771abdd1","tid":395314,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39956fbc56d06476156032283e2d686e764fce6","tid":395314,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:00:18.000Z","msg":"tornado=龍捲風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}